videos.description: Anfernee McLemore comes up with the huge rejection and Bryce Brown caps the fast break with a finger roll finish.
videos.headline: McLemore's block triggers Brown's layup

videos.description: Jared Harper throws a lob from the 3-point line and Anfernee McLemore slams it home.
videos.headline: McLemore dunks lob pass from Harper

videos.description: Anfernee McLemore cleanse up the missed bucket by racing in to throw down a two-handed putback dunk.
videos.headline: McLemore throws down putback jam

videos.description: Jared Harper gets the steal and throws a lob to Malik Dunbar for a sweet jam to cap the fast break.
videos.headline: Dunbar throws down sweet transition dunk

videos.description: Chuma Okeke takes flight off the dribble to throw down a vicious dunk over the help defender.
videos.headline: Okeke throws down monster dunk on defender
